The method should return an integer value representing the sum of the squares of all special elements in the `nums` array.
The method should not modify the input array `nums`.
The method should handle both positive and negative integers in the `nums` array.
The method should handle zero values in the `nums` array.
The method should handle duplicate elements in the `nums` array.
The method should handle large values in the `nums` array without causing overflow or underflow errors.
